# Build context for docker/tools.Dockerfile (repo root). BuildKit prefers this
# per-Dockerfile ignore over the root .dockerignore (which is scoped to the
# repo-root context and also covers the bitcoind node image). Allowlist only
# what the workspace build needs so the upload stays small — no .git, no
# target/ dirs (GBs after local builds).
*
!Cargo.toml
!Cargo.lock
!.cargo
!crates
